											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Isobel approaches her eagerly. [ChadD] Shoot whole sequence.  Aylin takes off her halm and lowers it before casting it aside. Her armor begins to glitter and fade.  Aylin is unsteady on her feet, drops to her knees. Armor and wings fading. Isobel closes the distance as Aylin says her line." />
