											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[ChadD] Shoot whole sequence. After &quot;in this moment,&quot; (pause VO) Aylin urgently kisses Isobel. Aylin abruptly lifsts Isobel as she bellows &quot;I want for nothing!&quot;  Both laughing, Isobel still lifted up in Aylins arms, Aylin spins them clockwise. As they spin nightsons wings manifest again before the screen fades to white." />
